address2: No. 239, Anna Salai Post Box No. 727
longBusinessSummary: K.C.P. Sugar and Industries Corporation Limited, together with its subsidiaries, manufactures and sells sugar and related products in India and internationally. It provides bio fertilizers, rectified spirit, extra neutral alcohol, ethanol, surgical sprit, organic manure, mycorrhiza vam, calcium lactate, and carbon dioxide. The company also manufactures liquidsolid separation equipment for industrial and environmental applications; processes urad dal; and offers research services in the areas of agriculture, chemical, and biotechnology. In addition, it operates cogeneration plant in Vuyyuru, Krishna District, Andhra Pradesh. The company also exports its products. K.C.P. Sugar and Industries Corporation Limited was incorporated in 1995 and is based in Chennai, India.
longName: K.C.P. Sugar and Industries Corporation Limited
